# Architecture

Stack: Docker (musicbrainz/musicbrainz-server:v30)
Mode: DB_ONLY=1 (web server disabled)
Main container: musicbrainz-db (PostgreSQL)
Helper container: musicbrainzkpi (scripts + KPI generation)
Volume: /var/lib/postgresql/data (persistent)
Dump location: /dbdump (mounted in musicbrainz-db)
Resources: ≥ 8 GB RAM, ≥ 80 GB disk
